						               													<description>From the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A Eron Dal Molin's board game, launched by Lends and developed by Foka Games. &amp;#10;In this fun journey, you're a pirate or a vampire shark alternately. As a pirate, mark points by surviving the attacks from the monster; as shark-vampire, gain victory points biting and turning pirates into new sharks. In both roles, just outsmart your opponents to win. It is a strategy game the escape tension is a constant and &amp;quot;backstabbing&amp;quot; among participants ensure laugh. Of course, a little luck can help in difficult situations.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every turn the pirates can move 1-3 sea spaces swimming away from vampire shark and block the path of another pirates. Blocked pirates are easy to be bitten by vampire sharks that need to move 3 sea spaces straight to the closest pirate. Strategy cards can be played to help pirates avoid bites or by vampire sharks to move freely. At same time a treasure hunt is happening and as a pirate you need to take the treasure map and go to the right island to gain more victory points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Being the last pirate alive you'll gain victory points so every turn you need to choose run away or block your friends.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
